Doc: The method of FRA discounting, if any, that will apply.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The method of FRA discounting, if any, that will apply.
 #/
enum FpML5.confirmation.FraDiscountingEnum {
    # "FRA Discounting" per the ISDA Definitions will apply.
    ISDA 
    # FRA discounting per the Australian Financial Markets Association (AFMA) OTC Financial Product Conventions will apply. Note: Should not be used for a FRA trade documented under a legal framework where the 2006 ISDA Definitions have been incorporated.
    AFMA 
    # No discounting will apply.
    NONE 
    # Per ISDA 2006 Definitions, Section 8.4. Discounting, paragraph (e)
    ISDAYield 

}

ISDA.Doc: "FRA Discounting" per the ISDA Definitions will apply.
ISDA.Name: ISDA

AFMA.Doc: FRA discounting per the Australian Financial Markets Association (AFMA) OTC Financial Product Conventions will apply. Note: Should not be used for a FRA trade documented under a legal framework where the 2006 ISDA Definitions have been incorporated.
AFMA.Name: AFMA

ISDAYield.Doc: Per ISDA 2006 Definitions, Section 8.4. Discounting, paragraph (e)
ISDAYield.Name: ISDAYield
